@Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5204

### Get tenant by slug
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/tenants/by-slug/acme
Accept: application/json

### Get tenant by ID
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/tenants/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

### Create tenant
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/tenants
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "slug": "acme",
  "name": "Acme Corp",
  "plan": "Free",
  "billingEmail": "billing@acme.com"
}

### Check slug availability
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/tenants/slug-exists?slug=acme
Accept: application/json
